  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Gift of Education - Learning Can&apos;t Wait</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We&apos;ve established 79 primary and 7 secondary schools in remotest areas of Bangladesh where previously there was no government school. Our students have continuously outperformed the national average. Key to our success is to hire and train teachers from the community. Using pre-fabricated structures, our schools are easily dismantled and relocated in the event of a natural disaster to quickly resume classes. To bypass the isolation, we use ICT-aided classrooms powered by solar panels.</narrative>
  </description>
